OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FBoth men are expected to be omitted
OL,8,Ffrom the second Test at the Kia Oval,
OL,9,Fwhich begins on June 17, a serious
OL,10,Fstep for a player of Stokes' stature
OL,11,Fand one that would cast his leadership
OL,12,Fposition into doubt.
OL,14,FIt was later reported an unnamed
OL,15,FSaracens rugby player was involved in
OL,16,Fan altercation involving the
OL,17,Fcricketers, as well as another member
OL,18,Fof ECB staff, with the Gallagher Prem
OL,19,Fclub initiating its own probe.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FBy being out so late Stokes, who grew
OL,8,Fup in Cockermouth, and Atkinson had
OL,9,Fbroken the team's midnight curfew,
OL,10,Fwhich returned in response to
OL,11,Fcriticism of the side's
OL,12,Fprofessionalism and drinking habits
OL,13,Fover the winter.
OL,15,FThere is no suggestion of any police
OL,16,Finvolvement but the sporting
OL,17,Fconsequences could be significant.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FSenior figures at the ECB were left
OL,8,Fshocked at the reputation the England
OL,9,Fteam has attracted in recent times,
OL,10,Fwith multiple reports of late night
OL,11,Fdrinking sessions on their doomed
OL,12,FAshes campaign, including a boozy trip
OL,13,Fto the beach resort of Noosa between
OL,14,Fthe second and third Tests.
OL,16,F"The ECB is currently investigating a
OL,17,Fbreach of team protocols following the
OL,18,Fconclusion of the first men's Test
OL,19,Fagainst New Zealand," read the
OL,20,Fgoverning body's statement.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
