OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,F"Ben Stokes and Gus Atkinson were
OL,8,Fpresent at a nightclub in the early
OL,9,Fhours of Monday morning when an
OL,10,Fincident took place. We are currently
OL,11,Fseeking further information and an
OL,12,Fannouncement regarding the squad for
OL,13,Fthe second Test will be made in due
OL,14,Fcourse. The Cricket Regulator has been
OL,15,Finformed and we will provide a further
OL,16,Fupdate when possible."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
