FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FIn 2017, Stokes was involved in an
OL,8,Fincident outside a Bristol nightclub
OL,9,Fthat resulted in him being charged
OL,10,Fwith affray. He then missed the Ashes
OL,11,Ftour of 2017-18 before he was cleared
OL,12,Fof the charge the following summer.
OL,14,FThe reports will come as a further
OL,15,Fembarrassment to the ECB, which has
OL,16,Fbeen at pains to show lessons have
OL,17,Fbeen learned following previous
OL,18,Fexcesses.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FHead coach Brendon McCullum has
OL,8,Fdefended his players over previous
OL,9,Fcriticism, but one of his most often
OL,10,Frepeated mantras since taking over in
OL,11,F2022 seems even more apt than ever.
OL,13,FSpeaking in Sri Lanka earlier this
OL,14,Fyear, McCullum said: "If you go back
OL,15,Fto the day I walked into the job, the
OL,16,Ffirst thing I said to these boys is,
OL,17,F'Don't do anything that lands you on
OL,18,Fthe front page of the paper and
OL,19,Fnothing good happens after midnight'.
OL,26,@vD@VOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,F"They're young guys who are growing up
OL,8,Fon the world stage under the brightest
OL,9,Flights and sometimes they're going to
OL,10,Fmake mistakes.
OL,12,F"We're just going to make sure that
OL,13,Fwe're looking after these guys whilst
OL,14,Falso occasionally using a firm grip to
OL,15,Fensure that we are not making those
OL,16,Fsame mistakes again."
OL,18,FStokes himself called for greater
OL,19,Fempathy when opener Ben Duckett was
OL,20,Fcaught on camera looking worse for
OL,21,Fwear after a drinking session in Noosa.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1781100697
OL,3,CBen Stokes' future as England Test
OL,4,Ccaptain in doubt after nightclub
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,F"I've had some pretty good times over
OL,8,Fmy career. I've also had some pretty
OL,9,Ftough times," he said.
OL,11,F"I have first-hand experience of how
OL,12,Fthis can affect people. It's never a
OL,13,Fnice place to be in when not only the
OL,14,Fmedia world, but also the social media
OL,15,Fworld, is just piling on top of you.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@MO]sD@AOU
